PIXABAY LICENSE (THIRD-PARTY ASSETS)

All music and sound effects (SFX) in this project are sourced from Pixabay (https://pixabay.com/service/license-summary/) and are used under the Pixabay License.

The Pixabay License allows free use of content in personal and commercial projects. Attribution is not required, but credit is provided to the original creators for transparency.

These assets are used as part of a larger game project and are not redistributed as standalone files.

All audio files have been converted to .ogg format for performance reasons. Some files may have been trimmed or looped for gameplay purposes. Original sources remain credited below.

Only in `/audio/` directory `.import` files are tracked in Git, which reference the local audio files. The actual audio files are not tracked and are only included in the final build of the game.

