SFX
------------------------------------------------------------

Slime Squish – Floraphonic
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-slime-squish-5-218569/
Used when slime moves or detects player

Collect Points – Liecio
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-collect-points-190037/
Used when collecting items (gems/cherries)

Frog Croaking – Dragon Studio
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-frog-croaking-sound-effect-322956/
Used when frog enemy moves or detects player

Retro Explode – Driken5482
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-retro-explode-1-236678/
Used when an enemy is defeated

Sword Slash – 49053354
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-sword-slash-315218/
Used for player attack

Sword Clash Hit – Dragon Studio
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-sword-clashhit-393837/
Used when attacks hit enemies

Epic Dragon Roar – Dragon Studio
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-epic-dragon-roar-364481/
Used when boss is nearby

Fireball Whoosh – Floraphonic
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-fireball-whoosh-1-179125/
Used for fireball attack

Victory Chime – Scratchonix
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-victory-chime-366449/
Used for level/boss victory

Super Deep Growl – Freesound Community
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-super-deep-growl-86749/
Used for boss idle sound

8-bit Game Over Sound – Lesiakower
https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/film-special-effects-8-bit-game-over-sound-effect-331435/
Used on player death / game over

